<h2>Q3 2009</h2>

<p>We're halfway through 2009 and things are shaping up really nicely. The upcoming quarter should see the completion of Nova M5 and a good start on M6 as well, setting us up for a very productive final quarter of 2009 and a promising start to 2010, the year of Nova! As always, keep an eye on the blog as we'll be updating about features and other things.</p>

